    <string name="setup_desc_permissions"><![CDATA[AuraCast ko aapki awaaz sunne ke liye Microphone permission zaroori hai.

Yeh bhi zaroori hai:
• Phone State — call ke waqt mic automatically band karne ke liye
• Notifications — streaming status dikhane ke liye]]></string>
